  "text": "The second equation is the Liouville equation instead of the Fokker Planck one from before, with the difference that in this case pde is not semilinear in general anymore. We will show that the LWR model matches this set of vanishing viscosity mean field model for the system. The solution of the hyperbolic HJB is in the sense of viscosity solutions [CITATION_1] .",
